research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md:67:| `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` | `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j} b_{e,j}` | candidate | low-rank shared bottleneck 只改变 shared coarse 与 PK routing 的打分链路，expert cleanup 仍落在静态 expert 子库上；最终仍是静态库有限加权和 | 直接兼容 |
