research/history/round_summaries/round_0170.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，|E(x)|=ACTIVE_EXPERTS 很小；在线侧可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表/加权和 + 少量 routed expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。r166-r169 已基本回答当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线的几条最自然轻量轴：`K=110/111` 只有递减收益，`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=152` 会明显退化，`NUM_EXPERTS=48` 也明显退化，因此继续在同一 family 上做局部细扫的信息增量已经很低。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r152 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，直接测试“轻 low-rank trunk + 双 expert routed 子库、但去掉 residual cleanup”能否在约 0.24x total_cost 下形成比当前 `<0.25x` shared+routed anchor 更强的新兼容 Pareto 点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0170.json:88:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0263.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e^\u03c4(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\u3002\u5176\u4e2d {b_{e,i}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff0cE_pk(x) \u7531\u4e24\u8def product-key router \u7ed9\u51fa\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0cS_e^\u03c4(x) \u7531 expert \u5185 JumpReLU \u5f62\u6210\u5c40\u90e8\u7a00\u758f\u652f\u6301\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cleft/right product-key \u6253\u5206 -> \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7ee7\u7eed\u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u50cf `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u8fd9\u7c7b\u5e26 shared/trunk \u7684\u5bb6\u65cf\u53ea\u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk`\u3001`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` \u7b49 sample/batch-coupled family \u4ecd\u662f\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002r262 \u5df2\u628a\u771f\u5b9e compatible frontier \u5237\u5230 controller objective\u22480.277586 = cost 0.09x + exceed 0.187586\uff0cexact round-summary objective=0.281336 = exact cost 0.09375 + exceed 0.187586\u3002\u5f53\u524d objective \u6570\u503c\u4e0a\u4ecd\u4e3b\u8981\u7531 exceed \u4e3b\u5bfc\uff0c\u4f46\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e\u4e3b\u7ebf\u6539\u8fdb\u7684\u76f4\u63a5\u6765\u6e90\u5176\u5b9e\u662f width \u538b\u7f29\u5e26\u6765\u7684\u6210\u672c\u5de6\u79fb\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u6700\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u4e0d\u662f\u7acb\u523b\u518d\u5207\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u786e\u8ba4\u5728 `NUM_EXPERTS=1024` \u4e0b width knee \u80fd\u5426\u518d\u8de8\u4e00\u4e2a controller \u6210\u672c\u6863\u4f4d\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r262\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u628a `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u4ece 80 \u964d\u5230 56\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`K=32`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5f53\u524d PK \u4e3b\u7ebf\u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u80fd\u628a controller `total_cost_ratio` \u4ece 0.09x \u538b\u5230 0.08x\u3002\u6309\u672c\u5730 exact \u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\uff0c`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56` \u65f6 selection_accesses=180224\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=344064\u3001exact total_cost_ratio=0.08203125\uff0ccontroller \u4e24\u4f4d\u5c0f\u6570\u53e3\u5f84\u4e0b\u8bb0\u4e3a 0.08x\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u9884\u7b97\u3002\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d controller frontier\uff0c\u53ea\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.19758612871170044`\uff1b\u82e5\u8981\u540c\u65f6\u5237\u65b0 r262 \u7684 exact objective\uff0c\u5219\u9700 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.19930475`\u3002\u8fd9\u8bf4\u660e `80 -> 56` \u4e0d\u662f\u540c\u6863\u5185\u7684 exact \u5fae\u8c03\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u771f\u6b63\u80fd\u8ba9 leaderboard \u6210\u672c\u518d\u5de6\u79fb\u4e00\u6863\u3001\u540c\u65f6\u4ecd\u5141\u8bb8 exceed \u9002\u5ea6\u56de\u5f39\u7684\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf width-knee probe\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0067.json:41:      "如果 NUM_EXPERTS=64 改善很弱，则可较清晰判定当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在 routed capacity，后续应把预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或其他带 residual cleanup 的结构。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r79 与 r80 已连续给出清晰负信号：把 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从 0.25 提到 0.5 会变差，而去掉 low-rank trunk 的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 也明显弱于 matched `lowrank_expert_residual`，说明当前低到中成本带里 trunk 仍是必要组成，且更强 residual cleanup 比更高 expert-stage 预算更重要。相对 r76 仅把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 32 降到 24，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答当前最关键的低成本问题：既然 routed-only、shared-basis、stage split、以及 trunk-free staged 路线都未带来更优结构段，那么 `lowrank + expert + residual` 这条当前最强兼容主线还能否仅通过进一步压缩必要 trunk 宽度，在保持大部分质量的同时把 total_cost 再往左推一小段，并形成比 r76 更经济的新 Pareto 点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:20:    "summary": "Round 81 不再继续切 family，也不回到已给出负信号的 routed-only、shared-basis 或 trunk-free staged 线；而是回到当前最强兼容三段式主线做一次高信息量成本压缩 probe。以 r76 为 reference，只把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 32 降到 24，直接测试 low-rank trunk 的最小必要宽度是否还能再压，从而在低到中成本带建立更靠左的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 前沿点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:25:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r76 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这比继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上扫 `STAGE1_RATIO`、回到 `expert_topk`/`factorized_expert_topk`，或继续展开 `two_stage_residual_expert` 更符合当前证据，因为最近四轮已经分别否定了 shared-basis、routed-only lookup-budget、higher stage1 budget、以及 trunk-free staged 这四条解释；现在最值得回答的是当前主线里必要 trunk 宽度到底还能压多少。选择 24 而不是直接跳到 16，是为了先做一次更平滑的左移 probe，降低把 trunk 压过头而导致结论只剩“明显变差”的风险。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:35:      "`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 trunk 库 + 静态 expert 子库 + 静态 residual 补偿库上的有限加权和，兼容性为扩展兼容。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:38:      "按当前 cost proxy 代码路径估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=24 NUM_EXPERTS=64 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 仍显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，并应比 r76 进一步降低 encoder 与 deployment 中与 trunk 相关的成本。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:54:    "architecture": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:63:    "description": "Round 81 不再继续切 family，也不回到已给出负信号的 routed-only、shared-basis 或 trunk-free staged 线；而是回到当前最强兼容三段式主线做一次高信息量成本压缩 probe。以 r76 为 reference，只把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 32 降到 24，直接测试 low-rank trunk 的最小必要宽度是否还能再压，从而在低到中成本带建立更靠左的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 前沿点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:64:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r76 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这比继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上扫 `STAGE1_RATIO`、回到 `expert_topk`/`factorized_expert_topk`，或继续展开 `two_stage_residual_expert` 更符合当前证据，因为最近四轮已经分别否定了 shared-basis、routed-only lookup-budget、higher stage1 budget、以及 trunk-free staged 这四条解释；现在最值得回答的是当前主线里必要 trunk 宽度到底还能压多少。选择 24 而不是直接跳到 16，是为了先做一次更平滑的左移 probe，降低把 trunk 压过头而导致结论只剩“明显变差”的风险。",
