research/history/round_summaries/round_0090.json:43:      "如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 仍然表现很差，则说明当前 target 上 multi-expert routed-only 路线整体不值得继续，后续应把低成本结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0068.json:25:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r51 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 直接兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。选择这一步而不是继续细扫 `lowrank_expert_residual`，是因为当前阶段更需要回答纯 routed MoE-like 子库在低成本带是否还能形成独立 Pareto 段；主要风险是更大 expert 容量也可能带来与 r67 类似的吞吐回退，或说明容量并非当前瓶颈。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0068.json:41:      "如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 改善很弱或再次出现明显吞吐回退，则可较清晰判定纯 routed sublibrary 扩容在当前 target 上已接近饱和，后续预算应更多回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或其他带 residual cleanup 的结构。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0068.json:63:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r51 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 直接兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。选择这一步而不是继续细扫 `lowrank_expert_residual`，是因为当前阶段更需要回答纯 routed MoE-like 子库在低成本带是否还能形成独立 Pareto 段；主要风险是更大 expert 容量也可能带来与 r67 类似的吞吐回退，或说明容量并非当前瓶颈。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0112.json:41:      "如果 `K=80` 相比 r111 明显退化，则可初步判定当前 shared+routed 低成本线更接近 deployment knee，后续不应再继续降 K，而应回到 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 或切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0088.json:43:      "如果 `factorized_expert_topk` 不如 r74，则说明当前 target 上 shared-basis scorer 还不足以单独形成新前沿，后续应把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert` 这类带 residual cleanup 的方向。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0226.json:25:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e\u53c2\u6570\uff0c\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u4ee3\u7801\u6539\u52a8\u3002\u6ca1\u6709\u518d\u9009 `lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`whitened_lowrank_residual`\u3001`codebook_topk` \u7b49\u672a\u6d4b family\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u5b83\u4eec\u5728\u5f53\u524d matched recipe \u4e0b\u90fd\u843d\u5728 `0.38x+`\uff0c\u5df2\u7ecf\u5728 objective \u4e0a\u5148\u9a8c\u65e0\u6cd5\u5237\u65b0 incumbent\uff1b\u7ee7\u7eed\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5b83\u4eec\u66f4\u50cf\u8d28\u91cf\u951a\u70b9\uff0c\u4e0d\u7b26\u5408\u672c\u8f6e\u201cmatched architecture probe\u201d\u4f18\u5148\u56de\u7b54 objective \u69fd\u4f4d\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u8981\u6c42\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4 `topk` \u4e0e `group_topk`\uff0c`jumprelu` \u5728\u540c exact cost \u4e0b\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u6700\u660e\u786e\u7684\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u53d8\u5316\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u66f4\u9ad8\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u540c\u6837\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u5b83\u8981\u8d62\u8fc7 r212 \u9700\u8981\u628a exceed \u76f4\u63a5\u6253\u5230\u7ea6 `0.0665`\uff0c\u73b0\u5b9e\u95e8\u69db\u5f88\u9ad8\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u8fd9\u66f4\u50cf\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u4e2a direct-compatible selector closure probe\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u9ad8\u7f6e\u4fe1\u7ffb\u76d8\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0226.json:36:      "\u5f53\u524d `0.19x~0.21x` matched architecture probes \u4e5f\u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u90fd\u6ca1\u628a objective \u62c9\u56de r212 \u9644\u8fd1\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0226.json:73:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e\u53c2\u6570\uff0c\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u4ee3\u7801\u6539\u52a8\u3002\u6ca1\u6709\u518d\u9009 `lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`whitened_lowrank_residual`\u3001`codebook_topk` \u7b49\u672a\u6d4b family\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u5b83\u4eec\u5728\u5f53\u524d matched recipe \u4e0b\u90fd\u843d\u5728 `0.38x+`\uff0c\u5df2\u7ecf\u5728 objective \u4e0a\u5148\u9a8c\u65e0\u6cd5\u5237\u65b0 incumbent\uff1b\u7ee7\u7eed\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5b83\u4eec\u66f4\u50cf\u8d28\u91cf\u951a\u70b9\uff0c\u4e0d\u7b26\u5408\u672c\u8f6e\u201cmatched architecture probe\u201d\u4f18\u5148\u56de\u7b54 objective \u69fd\u4f4d\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u8981\u6c42\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4 `topk` \u4e0e `group_topk`\uff0c`jumprelu` \u5728\u540c exact cost \u4e0b\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u6700\u660e\u786e\u7684\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u53d8\u5316\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u66f4\u9ad8\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u540c\u6837\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u5b83\u8981\u8d62\u8fc7 r212 \u9700\u8981\u628a exceed \u76f4\u63a5\u6253\u5230\u7ea6 `0.0665`\uff0c\u73b0\u5b9e\u95e8\u69db\u5f88\u9ad8\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u8fd9\u66f4\u50cf\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u4e2a direct-compatible selector closure probe\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u9ad8\u7f6e\u4fe1\u7ffb\u76d8\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0239.json:26:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5 `expert_jumprelu` \u505a\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u7ec6\u626b\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u72b6\u6001 `consecutive_no_improve=2` \u5207\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u7b26\u5408\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7b56\u7565\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u524d\u8005 combined_accesses=802816\u3001total_cost_ratio=0.19140625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f18\u5148\u7684 0.14x-0.20x \u5e26\uff1b\u540e\u8005\u4f1a\u76f4\u63a5\u5230 0.44x\uff0c\u4fe1\u606f\u5bc6\u5ea6\u592a\u4f4e\u3002\u8be5 family \u4e0e\u73b0\u6709\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u662f\u91cd\u547d\u540d\uff1a\u5b83\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 expert-local top-k \u652f\u6491\u6362\u6210 `expert_jumprelu` \u5f0f\u5e73\u6ed1\u95e8\u63a7\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u6d4b\u8bd5 trunk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u8ba9 small-K \u8def\u7ebf\u7684 exceed \u9000\u5316\u66f4\u6162\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u4e5f\u5f88\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u8981\u5728 0.1914x \u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent 0.35449\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.1631 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4e0d\u4f4e\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4ecd\u505a\u4e0d\u5230\uff0c\u5c31\u5e94\u5feb\u901f\u4e0b\u8c03\u8fd9\u6761 lowrank+JumpReLU \u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u8865\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0239.json:78:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5 `expert_jumprelu` \u505a\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u7ec6\u626b\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u72b6\u6001 `consecutive_no_improve=2` \u5207\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u7b26\u5408\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7b56\u7565\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u524d\u8005 combined_accesses=802816\u3001total_cost_ratio=0.19140625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f18\u5148\u7684 0.14x-0.20x \u5e26\uff1b\u540e\u8005\u4f1a\u76f4\u63a5\u5230 0.44x\uff0c\u4fe1\u606f\u5bc6\u5ea6\u592a\u4f4e\u3002\u8be5 family \u4e0e\u73b0\u6709\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u662f\u91cd\u547d\u540d\uff1a\u5b83\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 expert-local top-k \u652f\u6491\u6362\u6210 `expert_jumprelu` \u5f0f\u5e73\u6ed1\u95e8\u63a7\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u6d4b\u8bd5 trunk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u8ba9 small-K \u8def\u7ebf\u7684 exceed \u9000\u5316\u66f4\u6162\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u4e5f\u5f88\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u8981\u5728 0.1914x \u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent 0.35449\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.1631 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4e0d\u4f4e\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4ecd\u505a\u4e0d\u5230\uff0c\u5c31\u5e94\u5feb\u901f\u4e0b\u8c03\u8fd9\u6761 lowrank+JumpReLU \u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u8865\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:18:    "summary": "Round 48 证明 blocker 还没有消除：`lowrank_expert_topk` 再次在 behavioral diff 阶段被误拦，而且这次 round summary 显示并没有真正落地代码补丁。当前优先级最高的是继续做最小 repair，而不是回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 再打磨一个低成本邻域点；先把 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 的分发修通，再重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe，才能把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的成败当成结构证据。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:41:      "如果 repair 后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0123.json:25:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r122 只改 `K`。这一步遵循运行规则里“连续两轮未形成明确新非支配点后要换轴或换 family”的要求，因为 r121 和 r122 都在同一 shared+routed 子线上，而本轮明确从 width 轴切到 deployment 轴。选择 `K=112` 而不是继续推 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=240/256`，是因为 r122 已经证明宽度回补有效，当前更关键的是判断这条更窄 recipe 的剩余瓶颈是在 width 还是在 lookup；选择 112 而不是直接 128，是为了把实验保留在低成本探索带内，避免过早跳到更高成本。主要风险是改善幅度仍不足以支撑这条 224-width 子线继续占用预算；但这同样有价值，因为它会明确告诉我们下一轮应回到更宽 shared+routed recipe，或切向 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0123.json:42:      "如果 `K=112` 改善很小，则可较清晰判定这条 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 子线开始更像 width-limited 或结构饱和；下一轮应切回更宽的已验证 shared+routed recipe，或转向 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照，而不是继续堆 `K`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0123.json:64:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r122 只改 `K`。这一步遵循运行规则里“连续两轮未形成明确新非支配点后要换轴或换 family”的要求，因为 r121 和 r122 都在同一 shared+routed 子线上，而本轮明确从 width 轴切到 deployment 轴。选择 `K=112` 而不是继续推 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=240/256`，是因为 r122 已经证明宽度回补有效，当前更关键的是判断这条更窄 recipe 的剩余瓶颈是在 width 还是在 lookup；选择 112 而不是直接 128，是为了把实验保留在低成本探索带内，避免过早跳到更高成本。主要风险是改善幅度仍不足以支撑这条 224-width 子线继续占用预算；但这同样有价值，因为它会明确告诉我们下一轮应回到更宽 shared+routed recipe，或切向 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 对照。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1)} γ_j(x) c_j，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r 是共享 low-rank trunk，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，r_1 = x - t(x) - Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r98 在 `K=96`、r99 在 `K=112` 上连续给出清晰正斜率，说明当前压缩版三段式结构仍然受 deployment lookup budget 限制，而不是已经在 `K=96` 附近饱和。相对 r99 仅将 `K: 112 -> 128`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，如果这条 family 的收益继续随 K 增长，那么 FVU 应进一步低于 r99 的 0.0973，并完成当前 `lowrank_expert_residual` deployment knee 的上沿定位。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:20:    "summary": "r98 和 r99 已经把压缩版 `lowrank_expert_residual` 从 `K=96` 推到 `K=112` 且持续改善，因此本轮不切 family，也不回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 routed-only 方向。以 r99 为 reference，只改 `K=128`，直接回答这条三段式主线在当前 recipe 下的 deployment budget 是否仍有显著质量收益，并完成 `K=96-128` 的上沿定位。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:35:      "r98 (`lowrank_expert_residual K=96 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32`) 到 r99 (`K=112`) 给出连续正斜率，说明当前压缩版三段式结构的收益不只来自 residual 是否存在，也仍受 deployment budget 影响。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:36:      "当前最有信息量的问题是 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在这套压缩 recipe 下的 K-knee 上沿，而不是继续回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做局部补点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:37:      "按当前 fresh cost 估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算，并处于允许的中低成本结构对照带。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:54:    "architecture": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0100.json:63:    "description": "r98 和 r99 已经把压缩版 `lowrank_expert_residual` 从 `K=96` 推到 `K=112` 且持续改善，因此本轮不切 family，也不回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 routed-only 方向。以 r99 为 reference，只改 `K=128`，直接回答这条三段式主线在当前 recipe 下的 deployment budget 是否仍有显著质量收益，并完成 `K=96-128` 的上沿定位。",
