research/history/round_summaries/round_0069.json:41:      "如果 `K=160` 明显退化，则说明当前 `expert_topk` 的收益仍较依赖较大的查表预算，后续应把更多低成本预算转回 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual`。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0050.json:18:    "summary": "当前最高优先级仍是消除重复 blocker，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上打磨低成本邻域点。r48、r49 连续两轮都显示 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在 behavioral diff 阶段被误拦，且 round summary 里 `touched_files=[]`、`patch_path=null`，说明修复并未真正落地；因此 Round 50 应继续做最小 repair，把 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 的分发修通，再重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0050.json:41:      "如果 repair 后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0129.json:44:      "如果结果只小幅优于 r128 但仍明显差于现有 `<0.5x` frontier，则可初步判定问题不只在 routed factorization，本方向优先级应下调，后续转回 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0183.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_two_stage_residual_expert",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0183.json:21:    "summary": "已新增 low-cost prototype `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`：用 full-dim shared coarse sparse stage 先吃主干，再让 routed experts 只做 residual cleanup，并完成 config whitelist、factory dispatch 与 AutoResearch override allowlist 接线。建议下一轮以 r165 为 reference，仅切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_two_stage_residual_expert`，在与当前 best `<0.25x` anchor 相同的 `K=108, EF=1` recipe 下做一次干净的 matched-cost architecture probe。该 family 的本地 exact smoke、override 校验、config-resolution 校验均已通过，成本自检为 `0.13x + 0.11x = 0.24x`，正好回答当前主问题：显式“shared 主干 + residual experts”分工能否在 low-cost 主战场打败现有 joint shared+routed anchor。",
