research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:20:    "summary": "Round 43 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 被 policy 的 behavioral-diff blocker 拦截，这一轮先不把预算继续投到被运行时策略卡住的 family，而是沿当前最强且已验证兼容的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 继续向低成本带延伸。以 r37 为参考仅下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 16，预计把总成本从约 1.06x 压到约 0.52x，直接回答这条三段式结构在接近 0.5x 区域是否还能保持明显优于现有低成本 anchor 的质量。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:35:      "`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是 trunk 静态库 + expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:36:      "按当前实现的成本估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=16` 的 encoder≈0.32x、deployment≈0.20x、total≈0.52x，仍在 1.5×h×n 硬约束内。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:53:    "architecture": "lowrank_expert_residual",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:62:    "description": "Round 43 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 被 policy 的 behavioral-diff blocker 拦截，这一轮先不把预算继续投到被运行时策略卡住的 family，而是沿当前最强且已验证兼容的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 继续向低成本带延伸。以 r37 为参考仅下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 16，预计把总成本从约 1.06x 压到约 0.52x，直接回答这条三段式结构在接近 0.5x 区域是否还能保持明显优于现有低成本 anchor 的质量。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:87:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_residual",
